Description

A magnificent five-bedroom lateral apartment occupying the entire floor plate within One Hyde Park Knightsbridge, the most distinguished and exclusive developments in the world,
designed for luxurious living on a grand scale., this exceptional residence blends contemporary sophistication with timeless elegance.



The apartment offers outstanding living and entertaining space, featuring two beautifully proportioned reception rooms including a grand formal drawing room a bespoke designer kitchen, private study, and two guest cloakrooms. Each of the five bedroom suites has been meticulously crafted with sumptuous finishes, bespoke wardrobes, and spa-inspired bathrooms.

Residents benefit from a world-class lifestyle with access to five-star amenities, including a private spa, swimming pool, fitness suite, 24-hour concierge, and secure valet parking. In addition, residents enjoy exclusive Mandarin Oriental managed services, offering the same exceptional standards of hospitality, discretion, and comfort associated with one of the world`s leading luxury hotel brands.

Perfectly positioned to overlook Knightsbridge and Hyde Park, this remarkable home represents the pinnacle of Prime Central London living.

Candy & Candy, world-renowned for their uncompromising attention to detail and style, have exclusively designed all the communal areas of the building, including the superb spa and recreation facilities, the grand double-height reception lobby, the Park Library and the Serpentine Suite.

Additional benefits of this building is that it also comes with underground parking, wine cellar, storage unit and access to 24/7 concierge desk and Mandarin Oriental residents service. Furthermore, there is an exclusive on-site leisure and spa facilities at One Hyde Park which includes a private cinema, private events room for large parties, virtual experience room, squash court, gym, two private exercise studios, 21 metre ozone pool, Jacuzzi, two saunas, two steam rooms and two treatment rooms with en-suite relaxation rooms.



Notice
Please note we have not tested any apparatus, fixtures, fittings, or services. Interested parties must undertake their own investigation into the working order of these items. All measurements are approximate and photographs provided for guidance only.

About Global 1, London

23 Berkeley Square, Mayfair, London, W1J 6HE
Industry affiliations:

Global 1, international bespoke luxury real estate & lifestyle company head quartered in London. Dedicated to advising Ultra high-net-worth individuals (HNWIs) in the acquisition, sale, and letting of super-prime and luxury properties. Our expertise span international markets, with London our home city covering super prime residential areas, Belgravia, Hampstead, Holland Park, Hyde Park, Knightsbridge, Marylebone, Mayfair, Notting Hill, Regents Park, St James, St Johns Wood, and also encompassing the home counties.

Additionally, we offer a wide range of luxury lifestyle services, which can be found on our website.

We cater to a diverse clientele comprising (UHNWIs), developers, property funds, corporate institutions, sovereign wealth funds, and family offices globally who value our sourcing ability for privately marketed properties, trophy assets & highly sought-after investment opportunities.

Our proven track record of achieving record sales figures and sourcing premier on- and off-market properties has cemented our reputation and fostered long-term, trusted relationships with our clients. They value our deep market insights, extensive experience, professional approach, and our adeptness at managing their expectations. Our dynamic and seasoned team boasts unparalleled knowledge of the real estate market. We possess a keen understanding of the nuanced needs of our discerning international clientele and are adept at navigating cultural differences to meet our clients' exacting requirements.

Our Redress scheme is with PRS (Property Redress Scheme) and our CMP is with Client Money Protect. For more information please see our website.
